name: لما بدا يتثنى | Mader (2/2)
description: "لما بدا يتثنى/When my love began to sway" is the second piece from the Mader Conceptual Music series. "Mader" is a conceptual music Collection inspired by " Mawwal" recording made in the Levant area in the middle east from the 1910 - 1920 period. Back then, certain sound researchers arrived in the middle east and started recording all they could find. The quality was of the stone age, but the music still lives until today. Original Music by: Smokable. Original Artwork by Smokable.
